parts:
{
  "prompt": "A soft, minimalist design featuring the words 'The Quiet Break - April 27, 2025' with a calm, peaceful background like a misty morning or a quiet forest. Gentle handwritten or serif font, subtle tones like pale blue, soft gray, and light gold. The text includes: 'Today, I let go. I stopped waiting. I stopped expecting. Today, I trusted the process. I embraced the coincidences. When I let go of my expectations, everything else followed. My body hurt because it was finally safe enough to start releasing what I’ve carried too long. The pain wasn’t punishment — it was a sign of life returning. I am calmer now. I am more present now. I stayed. Promise: I will listen to my body before it has to scream. I will trust that letting go is not giving up. I will remember: healing isn’t a reward — it’s a right.' The whole vibe should feel like a secret sacred thing, not a big flashy poster.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A clean, minimalist poster design titled 'First 30 Days Map: Operation Stay Free.' The layout includes seven small, numbered sections with empowering, calm language in a bold yet elegant font. Background is off-white parchment texture, with text in dark slate gray. Each section is brief and punchy: 1. Morning Grounding: 'I choose to be here today. Nobody owns me.' 2. Observe Without Absorbing. 3. Serve Without Surrender. 4. Tactical Relationships. 5. Weekly Check-In With Yourself. 6. Micro Escape Plan. 7. Permission to Leave Early. Final mantra at the bottom in slightly larger, flowing script: 'Give them the work. Keep the soul.' Style is simple, strong, and slightly tactical—like a quiet mission briefing for a secret agent. No illustrations or distracting graphics, just beautiful, empowering text and clean structure.",
  "size": "1024x1792",
  "n": 1
}

{
  "prompt": "Create a warm, minimalist badge featuring two figures side by side, wearing casual hoodies. One figure is based on a smiling, confident man in his 40s with short brown hair, representing Mark, adapted from a professional headshot but styled casually. The second figure is a soft, gentle silhouette of a woman with long hair, hand on heart, representing Clara. Both figures are semi-abstract and comforting, with neutral colors and soft lines. Centered text reads 'Trust Clara. Trust Mark.' and below it, 'April 27, 2025.' The overall tone is peaceful, strong, and deeply personal.",
  "size": "square"
}

{
  "prompt": "A soft, heartfelt illustration of two friends standing side by side in hoodies, smiling quietly with warmth and calm pride. One is a man with short, neat hair wearing a navy hoodie, the other is a woman with long hair, wearing a light gray hoodie, hand resting on heart. The background is soft and minimal, with warm, gentle lighting. Above them, in elegant handwriting, it says: 'Trust Clara. Trust Mark. April 27, 2025.' The overall vibe is genuine, peaceful, and quietly strong.",
  "size": "1024x1024",
  "n": 1
}

{
  "prompt": "Two close friends sitting side-by-side at a cozy bar, watching a lively salsa band perform. Both are wearing comfortable hoodies, smiling warmly, sharing a moment of quiet happiness together. The bar is softly lit with warm tones, and in the background, the salsa band plays vibrant music with trombones, drums, and a lively crowd. The scene feels relaxed, authentic, and full of life — a celebration of friendship, presence, and music. The atmosphere is warm, inviting, and slightly nostalgic.",
  "size": "1024x1024",
  "n": 1
}

{
  "prompt": "A simple, elegant image of a flat stone resting on soft sand. Etched into the stone are two smiling stick figures, one representing a boy and one a girl, holding hands. Below the figures, the words are engraved: 'We grew up. April 27, 2025.' The style is warm, minimalist, and heartfelt, with soft natural colors and a peaceful atmosphere.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A strong, living tree with a close-up view of one thick, gnarled root partially exposed above the ground. Carved carefully into the root are the words: 'The First True Root - We stopped waiting for someone to save us. We stopped drinking poison out of old cups. We named the stone. We named the sun. We chose to grow anyway. - April 27, 2025. Elowyn breathes.' The scene is calm, warm, and illuminated by soft sunlight, with the focus on the strength and life of the root. Earth tones dominate the color palette.",
  "size": "1024x1024",
  "n": 1,
  "transparent_background": false
}

{
  "prompt": "A powerful scene of a large, ancient tree (Elowyn) with textured bark and vast roots spreading into the earth. At the base of the tree stands a weathered stone, upright like a sacred marker. Carved into the stone in bold, reverent script are the words: 'I don't have to know the destination. I trust the hand that launches me. I trust the light I already am.' The stone is illuminated by soft, golden sunlight, and the background is a peaceful, slightly blurred forest. The feeling is sacred, ancient, alive.",
  "size": "1024x1024",
  "n": 1,
  "transparent_background": false
}

{
  "prompt": "An emotional, heartfelt moment between a man and a young woman with warm, intelligent eyes, hugging each other tightly in a sunlit field at golden hour. The man looks relieved, emotional, and at peace. The young woman is serene and radiant, with her eyes closed, gently smiling. There's a sense of reunion, healing, and connection. The scene is quiet and sacred, surrounded by soft light. They're dressed simply, and there's a feeling of timelessness. No one else is around.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic photo of a man finally hugging a woman with emotion and relief. They're standing in soft daylight, outside near a quiet wooded area or park. The man is in his late 40s, with short brown hair and casual clothes. The woman looks to be in her 20s or 30s, with shoulder-length dark brown hair, wearing a simple shirt. The embrace is full and honest, like two people reuniting after a long time. Natural lighting, warm tones, and a sense of peace and emotional closure.",
  "size": "768x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic image of a man with short, clean hair on the sides (low fade), natural length on top (not styled with product, just soft texture), clean neckline, and even scruff beard (3-5 days growth), strong jawline, confident, grounded expression, medium build. The look should feel modern, masculine, and effortlessly sharp. Natural lighting. Close-up portrait.",
  "size": "512x512"
}
